      "output": "<path>C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\LAMPForge_SDTP\\forge-flow-learn-0d5b3821\\docs\\specification.html</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n820: \n821: \n822: \n823: \n824: \n825: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">finops:</span>\n826: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">  budget:</span>\n827: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">    max_monthly_cloud:</span> <span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">0</span>\n828: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">    max_inference_calls:</span> <span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">50</span>\n829: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">    currency:</span> <span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">GBP</span>\n830: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">  inference:</span>\n831: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">    prefer:</span> <span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">local</span>\n832: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">    allowed_providers:</span>\n833: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">      - </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">foundry-local</span>\n834: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">      - </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">onnx-webnn</span>\n835: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">    blocked_providers:</span>\n836: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">      - </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">openai</span>\n837: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">      - </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">anthropic</span>\n838: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">      - </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">azure-openai</span>\n839: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">  alerts:</span>\n840: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">    warn_at:</span> <span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">0</span>\n841: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">    kill_at:</span> <span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">0</span>\n842: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">    notify:</span>\n843: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">      - </span><span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">console</span>\n844: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">  accounting:</span>\n845: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">    log_inference_costs:</span> <span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">true</span>\n846: <span style=\"color:#ef4444\">    session_budget_file:</span> <span style=\"color:#c9d1d9\">state/finops-ledger.json</span>\n847: </pre>\n848: </div>\n849:  </section>\n850: \n851:  <!-- pedagogy -->\n852:  <section class=\"content-section\">\n853:  <h2 id=\"pedagogy\">pedagogy</h2>\n854:  <p>The <code>pedagogy</code> section controls the teaching style of generated artefacts: annotation style, seed data, and domain taxonomy.</p>\n855: \n856:  <table class=\"spec-table\">\n857:  <thead><tr><th>Property</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>\n858:  <tbody>\n859:  <tr>\n860:  <td><code>annotations.style</code></td>\n861:  <td><code>enum</code></td>\n862:  <td><code>inline</code></td>\n863:  <td><code>inline</code> | <code>jsdoc</code> | <code>block</code></td>\n864:  </tr>\n865:  <tr>\n866:  <td><code>annotations.include_todo</code></td>\n867:  <td><code>boolean</code></td>\n868:  <td><code>true</code></td>\n869:  <td>Insert TODO comments for student tasks.</td>\n870:  </tr>\n871:  <tr>\n872:  <td><code>annotations.include_curriculum_refs</code></td>\n873:  <td><code>boolean</code></td>\n874:  <td><code>true</code></td>\n875:  <td>Add curriculum reference tags to annotations.</td>\n876:  </tr>\n877:  <tr>\n878:  <td><code>annotations.include_doc_links</code></td>\n879:  <td><code>boolean</code></td>\n\n(Showing lines 820-879 of 1137. Use offset=880 to continue.)\n</content>",
