      "output": "<path>C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\LAMPForge_SDTP\\forge-flow-learn-0d5b3821\\docs\\examples.html</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n100:   version: \"1.0.0\"\n101: \n102: supervisor:\n103:   scaffold_level: 3\n104:   explainer_mode: true\n105:   visual_grammar:\n106:     enabled: true\n107:     theme: \"high-contrast\"\n108: \n109: finops:\n110:   budget:\n111:     max_monthly_cloud: 0.00   # Enforce local only\n112:     currency: GBP\n113:   inference:\n114:     prefer: local\n115:     allowed_providers: [foundry-local]</code></pre>\n116:       </div>\n117:     </section>\n118: \n119:     <!-- Advanced Cloud -->\n120:     <section class=\"content-section\">\n121:       <h2 id=\"advanced\">Advanced Cloud Implementation</h2>\n122:       <p>This configuration is designed for university-level projects where low-cost cloud inference is required for more complex tasks.</p>\n123: \n124:       <div class=\"code-block\">\n125:         <div class=\"code-block-header\"><span class=\"code-block-lang\">yaml · university-cloud.forge</span><button class=\"copy-btn\">⧉ Copy</button></div>\n126:         <pre><code class=\"language-yaml\">protocol: SDTP/1.0\n127: project:\n128:   name: \"Distributed Systems Lab\"\n129:   version: \"2.4.0\"\n130: \n131: supervisor:\n132:   scaffold_level: 1   # Minimal hand-holding\n133:   explainer_mode: false\n134: \n135: finops:\n136:   budget:\n137:     max_monthly_cloud: 10.00\n138:     currency: USD\n139:   alerts:\n140:     warn_at: 5.00\n141:     kill_at: 9.50\n142:     notify: [console, email]\n143:   inference:\n144:     prefer: cloud\n145:     allowed_providers: [groq, cerebras, foundry-local]\n146:     blocked_providers: [openai, anthropic]</code></pre>\n147:       </div>\n148:     </section>\n149: \n150:     <!-- Air-Gapped / Exams -->\n151:     <section class=\"content-section\">\n152:       <h2 id=\"exams\">Exam Mode (Air-Gapped)</h2>\n153:       <p>A strictly locked-down configuration for use in monitored assessment environments (e.g., WJEC Controlled Assessment).</p>\n154: \n155:       <div class=\"code-block\">\n156:         <div class=\"code-block-header\"><span class=\"code-block-lang\">yaml · wjec-exam.forge</span><button class=\"copy-btn\">⧉ Copy</button></div>\n157:         <pre><code class=\"language-yaml\">protocol: SDTP/1.0\n158: project:\n159:   name: \"A-Level NEA Project\"\n160:   id: \"STUDENT-99128\"\n161: \n162: supervisor:\n163:   scaffold_level: 0   # No AI assistance allowed\n164:   explainer_mode: false\n165:   audit_trail:\n166:     enabled: true\n167:     integrity_check: \"sha256\"\n168: \n169: finops:\n170:   budget:\n171:     max_monthly_cloud: 0.00\n172:   inference:\n173:     prefer: local\n174:     allowed_providers: []  # All AI blocked\n175:     blocked_providers: [foundry-local, onnx-webnn, groq, openai]</code></pre>\n176:       </div>\n177:     </section>\n178: \n179:     <!-- Navigation -->\n180:     <section class=\"content-section\">\n181:       <div class=\"quick-cards\">\n182:         <a href=\"learning.html\" class=\"quick-card\">\n183:           <div class=\"quick-card-icon\">📖</div>\n184:           <div class=\"quick-card-title\">Learning Environment</div>\n185:           <div class=\"quick-card-desc\">SDX for classrooms</div>\n186:         </a>\n187:         <a href=\"implementors.html\" class=\"quick-card\">\n188:           <div class=\"quick-card-icon\">🔧</div>\n189:           <div class=\"quick-card-title\">Implementors Guide</div>\n190:           <div class=\"quick-card-desc\">Build a .forge runtime</div>\n191:         </a>\n192:       </div>\n193:     </section>\n194:   </div>\n195: </div>\n196: </body>\n197: </html>\n\n(End of file - total 197 lines)\n</content>",
