      "output": "<path>C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\LAMPForge_SDTP\\forge-flow-learn-0d5b3821\\docs\\ARCHITECTURE.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # System Architecture\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: LAMPForge follows a **client-heavy architecture** where the browser is the primary compute surface. All code generation, SQL execution, and evidence logging happen client-side. The only server-side component is the AI blueprint generation edge function.\n6: \n7: ---\n8: \n9: ## High-Level Architecture\n10: \n11: ```mermaid\n12: graph TB\n13:     subgraph \"Browser Runtime\"\n14:         direction TB\n15:         \n16:         subgraph \"Pages\"\n17:             LP[LandingPage.tsx<br/>Intent + Scaffold]\n18:             PDE[PDEPage.tsx<br/>Unified PDE]\n19:             CP[CanvasPage.tsx<br/>Standalone Canvas]\n20:             WBP[WorkbenchPage.tsx<br/>Standalone Workbench]\n21:             EVP[EvidencePage.tsx<br/>Standalone Evidence]\n22:         end\n23:         \n24:         subgraph \"Code Generation Engine\"\n25:             SG[sql-generator.ts<br/>DDL + PHP + HTML]\n26:             FT[forge-types.ts<br/>Zod Schemas]\n27:         end\n28:         \n29:         subgraph \"AI Pipeline\"\n30:             FA[forge-ai.ts<br/>3-Stage Inference]\n31:         end\n32:         \n33:         subgraph \"IDE Surface (3-Tier)\"\n34:             COF[CodeOSSFrame.tsx<br/>Tier Detection]\n35:             OVS[OpenVSCode Server<br/>Tier 1 - Primary]\n36:             COS[Static Code-OSS<br/>Tier 2 - Legacy]\n37:             WCE[WebContainerEditor.tsx<br/>Tier 3 - Fallback]\n38:             VB[vscode-bridge.ts<br/>PostMessage + Config]\n39:             WCP[webcontainer-project.ts<br/>Project Builder]\n40:         end\n41:         \n42:         subgraph \"Panels\"\n43:             CLIP[CLIPanel.tsx<br/>Command Registry]\n44:             SQLP[SQLWorkbenchPanel.tsx<br/>sql.js + SQLite WASM]\n45:             EVPP[EvidencePanel.tsx<br/>Timeline View]\n46:             PTB[PanelToggleBar.tsx<br/>Visibility Controls]\n47:         end\n48:         \n49:         subgraph \"Canvas Nodes\"\n50:             EN[EntityNode.tsx]\n51:             TN[TransactionNode.tsx]\n52:             ON[OracleNode.tsx]\n53:             FSN[ForgeStatusNode.tsx]\n54:         end\n55:         \n56:         subgraph \"Communication\"\n57:             PDC[pde-channel.ts<br/>BroadcastChannel]\n58:         end\n59:     end\n60:     \n61:     subgraph \"Edge (Serverless)\"\n62:         EF[forge-schema/<br/>Edge Function]\n63:         AG[Lovable AI Gateway<br/>Gemini 3 Flash]\n64:     end\n65:     \n66:     subgraph \"Optional Local\"\n67:         OL[Ollama / Foundry Local<br/>Phi-4-mini]\n68:     end\n69:     \n70:     LP --> FA\n71:     FA --> OL\n72:     FA --> EF\n73:     EF --> AG\n74:     \n75:     FA -->|\"ForgeBlueprint\"| PDE\n76:     PDE --> SG\n77:     SG --> COF\n78:     PDE --> CLIP\n79:     PDE --> SQLP\n80:     PDE --> EVPP\n\n(Showing lines 1-80 of 276. Use offset=81 to continue.)\n</content>",
